    "A coffee with a friend. A concert that gave you chills. A tough conversation. Record it in seconds — no blank page, no pressure, no audience." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "A coffee with a friend. A concert that gave you chills. A tough conversation. Record it in seconds — no blank page, no pressure, no audience."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Un café avec un ami. Un concert qui t’a donné des frissons. Une conversation difficile. Conserve ces moments en quelques secondes : pas de page blanche, pas de pression, pas d'audience."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Add collection" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Add collection"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ajouter une collection"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Add emotions, people, and reflections to each pebble." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Add emotions, people, and reflections to each pebble."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ajoute des émotions, des personnes et des réflexions à chaque galet."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Add soul" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Add soul"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ajouter une âme"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Associate your moment with an emotion and a domain, relate with people and add your pebble to a stack or a collection." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Associate your moment with an emotion and a domain, relate with people and add your pebble to a stack or a collection."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Associe ton moment à une émotion et un domaine, relie-le à une âme, et ajoute ton galet à une pile ou une collection."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Bounce" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Bounce"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ricochet"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Bounce is a measure of your momentum over the last 28 days. It goes from level 0 (quiet) to level 7 (unstoppable).\n\nThe more days you record a pebble, the higher your Bounce. Miss a stretch and it eases back down — that's fine. It's a rhythm, not a score." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Bounce is a measure of your momentum over the last 28 days. It goes from level 0 (quiet) to level 7 (unstoppable).\n\nThe more days you record a pebble, the higher your Bounce. Miss a stretch and it eases back down — that's fine. It's a rhythm, not a score."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Le Ricochet mesure ton élan sur les 28 derniers jours. Il va du niveau 0 (calme) au niveau 7 (inarrêtable).\n\nEnregistre des galets chaque jour pour augmenter ton Ricochet. Sinon, il redescend doucement. L’important c’est la régularité."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Cancel" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
